# Contributing to Biocode Innovators AI Chatbot

Thank you for your interest in contributing! We are thrilled to have you here.

## How to Contribute
1. **Report Bugs:** Open an issue if you find a bug.
2. **Suggest Features:** Have an idea for bioinformatics or AI? Open an issue!
3. **Submit Code:** 
   - Fork the repository.
   - Create a new branch (`git checkout -b feature-name`).
   - Make your changes and test them.
   - Submit a Pull Request (PR) explaining your changes.

Together, we can make biological data and AI education more accessible!
